profile_summary: I'm Shravan Nander Pandala, a dedicated developer with a strong foundation in C, Python, and TypeScript, passionate about coding, learning, and contributing to open-source projects, with a keen interest in UI/UX design and front-end development, and experience in AI/ML. With 35 public repositories and a growing professional network, I'm committed to continuously improving my skills and collaborating with others to drive innovation. As a multifaceted developer, I bring a unique combination of technical expertise and creativity to the table, driven by a passion for grinding hard and delivering high-quality solutions.
